  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Benson Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Luke 12:11-12",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Luke 12:11-12",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "When they bring you unto the synagogues ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Let me add, however others may be affected by this testimony of the Spirit, one happy effect of its operation shall be to furnish you, my apostles, for a proper and honourable discharge of your office in its most difficult parts: and therefore when, in the opposition you shall meet with from your persecutors, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "they shall bring you into the synagogues, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "to be tried in the judicial courts assembled there; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And unto magistrates and powers ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Before greater magistrates and supreme powers, whether Jewish or heathen; — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Take ye no thought how ye shall answer ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Be not solicitous about the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "matter ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "or ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "manner ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "of your ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "defence, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "nor how to express yourselves. Though they may have not only your liberty but your lives in their hands, yet be not anxious what apology you shall make for yourselves, or what you shall advance in defence of the gospel you preach. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "For the Holy Ghost shall teach you ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— For in these seasons of the greatest difficulty and extremity, the Spirit of God shall suggest to your minds the answers you ought to give to the most captious inquiries, and most invidious charges of your enemies. Proper thoughts and expressions shall flow in upon you as fast as you can utter them, so that with undaunted courage you shall be able to vindicate the honour of the gospel, and to confound the most artful or most potent of your adversaries. See on ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 10:19-20",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Mark 13:11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
