    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And when they bring you unto the synagogues,.... Of the Jews, to be examined and scourged by the rulers of them: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and unto magistrates and powers; Heathen ones; the Persic version reads, \"princes and kings\"; and the Ethiopic version, \"princes, kings, and judges\"; see Matthew 10:18",
